<!--
  AI / LLM surface sitemap for jpcite.com.
  Aggregates the 16 canonical AI-discovery surfaces so answer engines and
  MCP-aware crawlers can fetch the full discovery cohort in one pass.

  This is additive to the master sitemap-index.xml; it does NOT replace any
  search-engine sitemap. URL set covers:
    - llms.txt cohort (4: JP/EN, summary/full) — llmstxt.org convention
    - OpenAPI agent profiles (2: full + gpt30 slim)
    - MCP discovery surfaces (3: mcp-server.json + .well-known/mcp/agents/ai-plugin)
    - Trust + provenance (3: trust.json + security.txt + sbom.json sources)
    - Cohort sitemaps cross-link (4: cases, laws, enforcement-cases, laws-en)
    - facts.html JP+EN (2)

  changefreq / priority hints follow sitemaps.org 0.9 spec; priorities are
  internal hints to AI crawlers, not Google PageRank.
-->
